https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/the-weeknd-medios-y-media-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weekend">Weeknd</a>似乎正在通过一系列神秘的社交媒体帖子来取笑一个新时代。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">周末 - &#39;Dawn FM&#39;评论：深情的明星与希望和事后见识</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位艺术家 - 真实姓名Abel Tesfaye  - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-teases-return-with-after-hours-and-dawn-fm-sequel-3567220">早在一月就一直在取笑他的回报</a>，这表明他即将到来的第六张唱片将是<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-after-hours-review-his-most-all-encompassing-record-to-date-is-also-an-existential-quandary-2632591">“小时”</a> / <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">“ Dawn FM”</a>三部曲的最后一部。他分别发布了2020年和2022年的两张专辑封面，然后是带有问号的照片。帖子的标题为“ 3”。</p><p>这位歌手还带着X/Twitter转发了一篇文章，上面写着：“痛苦，遗憾，重生”，他本人的三个不同的轮廓，这是最近在紫色的背景下向他展示了他小时候的。</p><p>现在，一个新的预告片暗示了一个新时代即将来临。一个简短的视频发布到了Weeknd的社交媒体上，他用玻璃眼睛凝视着相机。它伴随着晚上一些树林的照片。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C87hTc3PQPP/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div